FT  25 NOV 92 / Parliament and Politics: Pressure over environment audit
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
INCLUDING local authorities in EC requirements for environmental auditing
would dilute the proposed regulations and should be resisted, the Lords
environment committee heard yesterday.
