essentially follow Bethlehem's earlier plans, including installing a
continuous caster and a rod block at the local plant to increase efficiency
and production capability. Terms of the deal were not disclosed.
The bar, rod and wire operations bring in less than 10 per cent of
Bethlehem's annual sales of roughly Dollars 4bn.
Bethlehem said most of the bar, rod and wire operations were being sold as a
unit to preserve as many jobs as possible.
